title: California Gov. Gavin Newsom vetoes bill aimed at limiting the price of insulin
description: California Gov. Gavin Newsom has vetoed a bill aimed at limiting the price of insulin

title: A Baltic Sea gas pipeline between Finland and Estonia is shut down over a suspected leak
description: Operators noted an unusual drop in pressure in the pipeline early Sunday.

title: WATCH:  Gaza building collapses in Israeli airstrike after Hamas attacks
description: Video shows the moment a high-rise building in Gaza was struck by Israeli warplanes, spewing plumes of black smoke into the air.

title: Shooting at Pennsylvania community center kills 1 and injures 5 victims
description: Police in Pennsylvania say one person was killed and five were wounded in a shooting during a private party at a community center

title: American mountaineer, local guide dead after avalanches hit Tibetan mountain. Two others are missing
description: Chinese media reports have confirmed American mountaineer Anna Gutu and a Nepalese guide Mingmar Sherpa died after avalanches struck the slopes of the Tibetan mountain Shishapangma while two others remain missing
